      "text": "さくら？\nやけに上機嫌だが何かいいことでもあったのか？",
      "startTime": 6.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　サニピが出演するお正月のテレビ番組に\n芸人のホットドッグさんも出るって聞いて……",
      "startTime": 15.7463727315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そのことか\n企画コーナーでさくらと羽根つき対決するんだろ？",
      "startTime": 21.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです！\n大好きな芸人さんなので共演出来るのが嬉しくて！",
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばみんなは一時期\nレッスンの合間にお笑いのDVDをよく観ていたな",
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんが自然な笑顔になれるように\nいろいろ試してた頃ですね",
      "startTime": 40.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "あの時観たDVDが面白くって、それ以来ずっと\n私はホットドッグさんを応援してるんです",
